        IQueryBeanResult<Bean> performSearch(boolean isClearBundle)
        Parameters:
        isClearBundle - - if true, then the bundle of the ABContactSearchCriteria will be cleared before performing the search so that only the criteria is left in the bundle. Should set this to true if calling from UI because Pebbles will not clear the bundle when user stays on the same page. (See jira CC-28078 for more details) *
